inputs.name: Query
inputs.value:
AppServiceConsoleLogs 
| extend central_time = datetime_utc_to_local(TimeGenerated,'US/Central') 
| project central_time, JsonResult = parse_json(ResultDescription) 
| evaluate bag_unpack(JsonResult, ignoredProperties=dynamic(['@timestamp', 'BundleId', 'Entry Step', 'Entry Time', 'thread_name'])) 
| where level in ('ERROR') 
| project-reorder central_time, level, message
